  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1262">
<l>ilaṅkiḻā yiṉṟu maṟappiṉeṉ meṉṟōḷ </l>
<l> kalaṅkaḻiyuṅ kārikai nīttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O you bright-jewelled maid, if I forget (him) today, my shoulders will lose their beauty even in the other life and make my bracelets loose.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
